                      {
                        "name": "A_count",
                        "description": "Count and label the parts of the first or the top bar"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "dialogue": "Let me show you how to find one-half. [event: restore_snapshot_prompt_start] For one-half, we need exactly 2 equal parts with 1 part shaded. [event:A_count_shaded] The [event: A_select] top bar has 1 part shaded. [event:A_count] And it has exactly 2 equal parts total. That's what makes it one-half - 1 out of 2 equal parts.",
